comment: /**  * Map the response type to its JMX compliant counterpart.  * @param responseType the operation's response type  * @return the JMX compliant type  */
code: /**  * Map the response type to its JMX compliant counterpart.  * @param responseType the operation's response type  * @return the JMX compliant type  */ Class<?> mapResponseType(Class<?> responseType).

comment: /**  * Map the operation's response so that it can be consumed by a JMX compliant client.  * @param response the operation's response  * @return the {@code response}, in a JMX compliant format  */
code: /**  * Map the operation's response so that it can be consumed by a JMX compliant client.  * @param response the operation's response  * @return the {@code response}, in a JMX compliant format  */ Object mapResponse(Object response).
